NIFTIFile-class          package:NeuroImage          R Documentation

_C_l_a_s_s "_N_I_F_T_I_F_i_l_e"

_D_e_s_c_r_i_p_t_i_o_n:

     a class that handles input/output of NIFTI formatted image data

_O_b_j_e_c_t_s _f_r_o_m _t_h_e _C_l_a_s_s:

     Objects can be created by calls of the form 'new("NIFTIFile",
     ...)'.

_S_l_o_t_s:


     '_f_i_l_e_T_y_p_e': Object of class '"character"' : the file type  

     '_p_a_t_h': Object of class '"character"' : the file path  

     '_o_p_e_n': Object of class '"character"' : whether to open file for
          reading "r" or writing "w" 

_E_x_t_e_n_d_s:

     Class '"BrainFile"', directly.

_M_e_t_h_o_d_s:


     _d_a_t_a_F_i_l_e_E_x_t 'signature(x = "NIFTIFile")': returns the data file
          extension  

     _f_i_l_e_N_a_m_e 'signature(x = "NIFTIFile")': returns the file underlying
          file name  

     _f_i_l_e_T_y_p_e 'signature(x = "NIFTIFile")': returns the file type  

     _h_e_a_d_e_r_F_i_l_e_E_x_t 'signature(x = "NIFTIFile")': returns the header
          extension 

     _o_p_e_n_F_o_r 'signature(x = "NIFTIFile")': querues whether file is open
          for read or write 

     _p_a_t_h 'signature(x = "NIFTIFile")': the full path of the file  

     _r_e_a_d_D_a_t_a 'signature(x = "NIFTIFile", indices = "index")': reads
          the data and returns a class deriving from "BrainData" 

     _r_e_a_d_D_a_t_a 'signature(x = "NIFTIFile", indices = "missing")':  reads
          the data and returns a class deriving from "BrainData"

     _r_e_a_d_H_e_a_d_e_r 'signature(x = "NIFTIFile")': reads the header and
          returns a "NIFTIHeader" object  

     _w_r_i_t_e_H_e_a_d_e_r 'signature(x = "NIFTIFile",header = "BrainHeader")':
          writes supplied header argument to disk as NIFTIHeader  

     _w_r_i_t_e_D_a_t_a 'signature(x = "NIFTIFile",header = "NIFTIHeader",
          data="vector")': writes data vector to disk  

     _s_h_o_w 'signature(x = "NIFTIFile")': print a text representation of
          the 'NIFTIFile' object 

